Class Vector2i

java.lang.Object
com.rubynaxela.kyanite.core.system.Vector2i
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class Vector2i extends Object implements Serializable
Represents two-dimensional vectors using integer coordinates and provides arithmetic operations on integral 2D vectors.
